OUTTAKES: GRILL CRAZY 
Pathe Entertainment is stil trying o get clearances to use "Harley Davidson and 
the Marlboro Man" as a movie title. But the company has nailed down its stars: 
They'll play the title characters, two buddies who reunite to save an old pal's 
restaurant- "The Rock 'n' Roll Grill-when it's threatened by Aryan drug 
dealers. 
Filming begins this fall, with Simon Wincer directing for producer Jere 
Henshaw. John M. Wilson 
